                "invention-title": [
                    "Methane reforming hydrogen production device",
                    "一种甲烷重整制氢装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "A methane reforming hydrogen production device comprises a methane gas conveying unit, a water vapor conveying unit, a hydrogen production unit, a heat exchange unit, a hydrogen purification unit, a circulation unit and a methane extraction unit, and the methane gas conveying unit is used for conveying methane gas to the hydrogen production unit; the water vapor conveying unit is used for generating water vapor and conveying a proper amount of water vapor to the hydrogen production unit; the hydrogen production unit is used for promoting a reforming reaction of methane gas and water vapor to generate hydrogen and carbon monoxide; the heat exchange unit is used for recovering reaction heat of the hydrogen production unit and preheating methane gas and water vapor; the hydrogen purification unit is used for separating pure hydrogen from the gas mixture after the reforming reaction of the hydrogen production unit; the circulating unit is used for separating unreacted methane gas and circularly sending the unreacted methane gas back to the hydrogen production unit for further reforming reaction; the methane extraction unit is used for extracting pure methane gas, the device can recycle heat energy and methane gas, and energy consumption is effectively reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种甲烷重整制氢装置，包括甲烷气体输送单元、水蒸气输送单元、制氢单元、热交换单元、氢气纯化单元、循环单元和甲烷提取单元，甲烷气体输送单元用于输送甲烷气体至制氢单元；水蒸气输送单元用于产生水蒸气并输送适量的水蒸气至制氢单元；制氢单元用于促进甲烷气体和水蒸气发生重整反应生成氢气和一氧化碳；热交换单元用于回收制氢单元的反应热并用来预热甲烷气体和水蒸气；氢气纯化单元用于从制氢单元发生重整反应后的气体混合物中分离出纯净的氢气；循环单元用于将未反应的甲烷气体分离出来并将其循环送回制氢单元发生进一步的重整反应；甲烷提取单元用于提取纯净的甲烷气体，该装置回收可以回收利用热能和甲烷气体，有效减少能源消耗。"
                }
            ]
